<item>
            <title>[LU-18976] Correctly reports DNS resolution failures in lsvcgssd</title>
                <link>https://jira.whamcloud.com/browse/LU-18976</link>
                <project id="10000" key="LU">Lustre</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;When a DNS resolution fails, this is not reported as an error by lsvcgssd (it returns the IP address instead), but this is causing another error later, returning a strange error message.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;Use proper NI_NAMEREQD flag with getnameinfo() in lsvcgssd when resolving IP addresses, for it to return an error if DNS resolution fails.&lt;/p&gt;</description>
